00:33:04,820 --> 00:33:05,160
 jel da,

1025
00:33:05,160 --> 00:33:05,560
 ono,

1026
00:33:05,560 --> 00:33:06,920
 mišića i tako.

1027
00:33:06,920 --> 00:33:07,900
 I sad,

1028
00:33:07,900 --> 00:33:08,140
 pazi,

1029
00:33:08,140 --> 00:33:08,600
 on isto,

1030
00:33:08,600 --> 00:33:09,140
 ovaj,

1031
00:33:09,140 --> 00:33:11,260
 imao je valjda dan za trening,

1032
00:33:11,260 --> 00:33:14,940
 gdje je trebao trčati nekakvih deseta kilometara,

1033
00:33:14,940 --> 00:33:16,040
 i,

1034
00:33:16,040 --> 00:33:18,260
 frajer se obuko,

1035
00:33:18,260 --> 00:33:19,100
 znaš,

1036
00:33:19,100 --> 00:33:19,260
 one,

1037
00:33:19,260 --> 00:33:20,840
 ono usko,

1038
00:33:20,840 --> 00:33:21,760
 usko dijelo,

1039
00:33:21,760 --> 00:33:23,000
 za trčanje.

1040
00:33:23,000 --> 00:33:24,420
 Kako je,

1041
00:33:24,420 --> 00:33:24,700
 recimo,

1042
00:33:24,700 --> 00:33:25,220
 da,

1043
00:33:25,220 --> 00:33:25,400
 da,

1044
00:33:25,400 --> 00:33:25,720
 ono,

1045
00:33:25,720 --> 00:33:26,580
 ali s kratkim,

1046
00:33:26,580 --> 00:33:26,820
 ono,

1047
00:33:26,820 --> 00:33:27,420
 hlačicama,

1048
00:33:27,420 --> 00:33:27,900
 znaš,

1049
00:33:27,900 --> 00:33:29,140
 kakva koriste,

1050
00:33:29,140 --> 00:33:29,500
 recimo,

1051
00:33:29,500 --> 00:33:31,860
 za triatlon?

1052
00:33:33,040 --> 00:33:33,600
 E,

1053
00:33:33,600 --> 00:33:34,240
 i,

1054
00:33:34,240 --> 00:33:36,460
 frajer ti se u to obuko,

1055
00:33:36,460 --> 00:33:37,560
 i,

1056
00:33:37,560 --> 00:33:38,420
 i krenuo,

1057
00:33:38,420 --> 00:33:39,580
 i krenuo trčat,

1058
00:33:39,580 --> 00:33:40,560
 isto po cesti.

1059
00:33:40,560 --> 00:33:41,640
 To je bio šov.

1060
00:33:41,640 --> 00:33:42,260
 Znači,

1061
00:33:42,260 --> 00:33:42,580
 to je,

1062
00:33:42,580 --> 00:33:43,060
 on je,

1063
00:33:43,060 --> 00:33:43,400
 on je ljude,

1064
00:33:43,400 --> 00:33:47,120
 ljudi su iza njega išli u koloni i svirali namjerno.

1065
00:33:47,200 --> 00:33:47,680
 još je neka,

1066
00:33:47,680 --> 00:33:47,960
 neka,

1067
00:33:47,960 --> 00:33:48,020
 neka,

1068
00:33:48,020 --> 00:33:48,400
 neka,

1069
00:33:48,400 --> 00:33:49,260
 ono boja bila,

1070
00:33:49,260 --> 00:33:50,280
 ono,

1071
00:33:50,280 --> 00:33:51,000
 drečava,

1072
00:33:51,000 --> 00:33:52,380
 strašno nešto.

1073
00:33:52,380 --> 00:33:52,880
 Znači,

1074
00:33:52,880 --> 00:33:54,480
 oni su napravili spredačinu toga,

1075
00:33:54,480 --> 00:33:55,100
 oni su iza njega,

1076
00:33:55,100 --> 00:33:56,000
 nisu ga tijeli obići,

1077
00:33:56,000 --> 00:33:56,180
 znači,

1078
00:33:56,180 --> 00:33:56,940
 išli su iza njega,

1079
00:33:56,940 --> 00:33:57,860
 trubili mu,

1080
00:33:57,860 --> 00:33:58,860
 napravili šov,

1081
00:33:58,860 --> 00:33:59,620
 snimali ga,

1082
00:33:59,620 --> 00:34:00,520
 a on,

1083
00:34:00,520 --> 00:34:01,300
 on frajer,

1084
00:34:01,300 --> 00:34:01,480
 ono,

1085
00:34:01,480 --> 00:34:02,500
 do kraja išo od dnevna,

1086
00:34:02,500 --> 00:34:03,980
 on se nije dao smeste u tome,

1087
00:34:03,980 --> 00:34:04,640
 zamisli,

1088
00:34:04,640 --> 00:34:07,040
 kakva je to muževnošće,

1089
00:34:07,140 --> 00:34:09,480
 koja je to svijest o tome da si muškarac.

1090
00:34:09,480 --> 00:34:12,300
 Puno potreda,

1091
00:34:12,300 --> 00:34:13,120
 puno potreda.

1092
00:34:13,120 --> 00:34:13,940
 Da,

1093
00:34:13,940 --> 00:34:14,880
 puno potreda.

1094
00:34:14,880 --> 00:34:17,820
 Kruno,

1095
00:34:17,820 --> 00:34:19,420
 kako,

1096
00:34:19,420 --> 00:34:23,060
 spomenuo si sakramentalni život,

1097
00:34:23,060 --> 00:34:27,740
 kako jedan katolički muškarac koji još nije oženjen,

1098
00:34:27,740 --> 00:34:29,600
 pa i oni koji su oženjeni,

1099
00:34:29,600 --> 00:34:33,200
 ali recimo sada možda da se samo paziramo na one koji još nisu oženjeni,

1100
00:34:34,900 --> 00:34:38,740
 kako može istinski živjeti svoju muževnost,

1101
00:34:38,740 --> 00:34:47,020
 kako može otkriti tu svoju ulogu koju je dobio svojim začeđem,

1102
00:34:47,020 --> 00:34:52,360
 svojim krštenjem kao muškarac.

1103
00:34:52,360 --> 00:34:56,440
 Da, opet kompleksno pitanje,

1104
00:34:56,440 --> 00:34:58,200
 a jednostavno,

1105
00:34:58,200 --> 00:35:02,060
 prvo, ono što je meni već neko vrijeme na srcu,

1106
00:35:02,060 --> 00:35:03,180
 već nekoliko godina,

1107
00:35:03,180 --> 00:35:04,580
 znači taj odnos sa Bogom Otcem,

1108
00:35:04,900 --> 00:35:06,240
 znači ospostaviti taj odnos.

1109
00:35:06,240 --> 00:35:07,980
 Drugo je molitva,

1110
00:35:07,980 --> 00:35:09,680
 misa,

1111
00:35:09,680 --> 00:35:11,240
 sveto pismo,

1112
00:35:11,240 --> 00:35:16,060
 i jednostavno ući u to neko razmatranje,

1113
00:35:16,060 --> 00:35:18,480
 ući u promišljanje,

1114
00:35:18,480 --> 00:35:21,740
 sagledati sve te muške uloge,

1115
00:35:21,740 --> 00:35:24,020
 znači muškarci u svetom pismom,

1116
00:35:24,020 --> 00:35:26,680
 koji mogu biti uzori po mnogo čemu.

1117
00:35:26,680 --> 00:35:29,580
 Upravo mi sad pada na pamet kraj Zavid.

1118
00:35:29,580 --> 00:35:30,900
 Dakle,

1119
00:35:30,900 --> 00:35:33,580
 on je bio najmlađi,

1120
00:35:33,580 --> 00:35:36,300
 bio je najslabiji od sinova,

1121
00:35:36,300 --> 00:35:40,100
 možemo reći da je bio odbačen od svoga oca,

1122
00:35:40,100 --> 00:35:40,760
 dakle,

1123
00:35:40,760 --> 00:35:42,020
 je nosio tu neku ranu,

1124
00:35:42,020 --> 00:35:44,920
 a opet ga je Bog pomazao,

1125
00:35:44,920 --> 00:35:46,840
 znači da postane kralj,

1126
00:35:46,840 --> 00:35:49,800
 i da pobjedi tog Golijata,

1127
00:35:49,800 --> 00:35:51,760
 koji je kasnije došao.

1128
00:35:52,440 --> 00:35:53,640
 Tako da,

1129
00:35:53,640 --> 00:35:56,520
 uz taj odnos sa Bogom,

1130
00:35:56,520 --> 00:36:00,260
 uz taj neki sakramentalni život,

1131
00:36:00,260 --> 00:36:01,400
 dakle,

1132
00:36:01,400 --> 00:36:03,120
 Bog uistin može

1133
00:36:03,120 --> 00:36:04,720
 da nam dati tu snagu

1134
00:36:04,720 --> 00:36:07,020
 da pobjedimo te Golijate

1135
00:36:07,020 --> 00:36:08,140
 u svom životu,

1136
00:36:08,140 --> 00:36:10,860
 i da jednostavno uđemo u tu slobodu

1137
00:36:10,860 --> 00:36:12,660
 djeteta Božeg

1138
00:36:12,660 --> 00:36:13,640
 i na kraju

1139
00:36:13,640 --> 00:36:15,860
 pravog autentičnog muškarca.

1140
00:36:15,860 --> 00:36:18,420
 Dakle, tu bi sam mogo napisati romani

1141
00:36:18,420 --> 00:36:19,580
 i cijelo promišljanje,

1142
00:36:19,580 --> 00:36:21,260
 dizertacije o Davidu

1143
00:36:21,260 --> 00:36:22,720
 i sličnim junacima,

1144
00:36:22,720 --> 00:36:25,280
 ali to je ono što mi sad dolazi

1145
00:36:25,280 --> 00:36:26,320
 na pamet,

1146
00:36:26,320 --> 00:36:27,380
 da jednostavno

1147
00:36:27,380 --> 00:36:29,120
 treba

1148
00:36:29,120 --> 00:36:31,400
 klekut na koljena

1149
00:36:31,400 --> 00:36:33,400
 i dopustiti Bogu

1150
00:36:33,400 --> 00:36:34,500
 da on sve to voli,

1151
00:36:34,500 --> 00:36:35,340
 da nas upučujem.

1152
00:36:35,340 --> 00:36:36,640
 Evo ono što ja

1153
00:36:36,640 --> 00:36:38,220
 svakodnevno radim

1154
00:36:38,220 --> 00:36:40,280
 je da svaki dan učem neki citat

1155
00:36:40,280 --> 00:36:41,260
 iz svetog pisma.

1156
00:36:41,260 --> 00:36:42,620
 Znači, nam pisući citate,

1157
00:36:42,620 --> 00:36:43,160
 to znaš,

1158
00:36:43,160 --> 00:36:44,140
 izlučem neki citat,

1159
00:36:44,140 --> 00:36:44,900
 a pridle toga

1160
00:36:44,900 --> 00:36:46,600
 spomolom duhu svetom

1161
00:36:46,600 --> 00:36:47,820
 i tražim ovoga,

1162
00:36:47,820 --> 00:36:50,520
 da mi progovori za taj dan neku stvar.

1163
00:36:51,020 --> 00:36:51,760
 najčešće

1164
00:36:51,760 --> 00:36:52,880
 ni ne kažem

1165
00:36:52,880 --> 00:36:54,000
 svoju potrebu,

1166
00:36:54,000 --> 00:36:55,680
 a već kad izvučem citat,

1167
00:36:55,680 --> 00:36:56,020
 vidim

1168
00:36:56,020 --> 00:36:57,920
 da se to odnose na tu moju potrebu.

1169
00:36:57,920 --> 00:36:59,380
 Dakle, jednostavno treba

1170
00:36:59,380 --> 00:37:01,060
 se povezati

1171
00:37:01,060 --> 00:37:02,900
 s Bogu na sve moguće načine.

1172
00:37:03,400 --> 00:37:06,260
 i kad ispredeš tu mrežu

1173
00:37:06,260 --> 00:37:08,120
 svih tih stvari

1174
00:37:08,120 --> 00:37:09,500
 koje te neki način štite

1175
00:37:09,500 --> 00:37:11,140
 i uvode u taj misteri,

1176
00:37:11,140 --> 00:37:13,560
 u sve te pobožnosti,

1177
00:37:13,560 --> 00:37:15,740
 onda polako sazrijevaš

1178
00:37:15,740 --> 00:37:18,360
 u pravog kristovog vojnika

1179
00:37:18,360 --> 00:37:20,220
 i sina

1180
00:37:20,220 --> 00:37:21,580
 gdje te očeva?

1181
00:37:21,580 --> 00:37:26,100
 Pa ja

1182
00:37:26,100 --> 00:37:29,420
 nemam što na ovo dodati.

1183
00:37:29,420 --> 00:37:30,420
 Milina te slušati.

1184
00:37:30,420 --> 00:37:32,320
 Milina te slušati

1185
00:37:32,320 --> 00:37:34,280
 i baš mi je drago

1186
00:37:34,280 --> 00:37:35,600
 da smo uspjeli

1187
00:37:35,600 --> 00:37:37,860
 proći sve ove tehničke poteškoće,

1188
00:37:37,860 --> 00:37:38,760
 da si nam se uključio.

1189
00:37:38,820 --> 00:37:39,660
 Vjerujem da je i drugima

1190
00:37:39,660 --> 00:37:42,700
 ovo bilo na izgradnju

1191
00:37:42,700 --> 00:37:43,440
 i na blagoslov.

1192
00:37:43,440 --> 00:37:46,360
 Hajde samo još,

1193
00:37:46,360 --> 00:37:48,080
 evo, možda pitanje za kraj,

1194
00:37:48,080 --> 00:37:49,100
 a onda ćemo sa nekom

1195
00:37:49,100 --> 00:37:50,280
 završnom riječi završiti.

1196
00:37:50,280 --> 00:37:52,280
 Pa nije teško,

1197
00:37:52,280 --> 00:37:53,220
 nema mi neko teško pitanje.

1198
00:37:53,220 --> 00:37:54,180
 Pa nije teško,

1199
00:37:54,180 --> 00:37:55,980
 ali vidim da,

1200
00:37:55,980 --> 00:37:57,520
 kaže,

1201
00:37:57,520 --> 00:37:58,400
 Sunčica treba nam

1202
00:37:58,400 --> 00:38:00,140
 iz stranica za ženstvene budite.

1203
00:38:00,140 --> 00:38:01,360
 Imamo ženu vrsnu.

1204
00:38:01,360 --> 00:38:03,020
 Ako niste zapratili,

1205
00:38:03,020 --> 00:38:04,080
 zapratite ženu vrsnu.

1206
00:38:04,080 --> 00:38:04,960
 Žena vrsna je jedan

1207
00:38:04,960 --> 00:38:06,060
 fantastičan profil

1208
00:38:06,060 --> 00:38:07,300
 koji baš čini to.

1209
00:38:08,660 --> 00:38:13,160
 Jel muškarci plaću?

1210
00:38:13,160 --> 00:38:14,800
 Jeli,

1211
00:38:14,800 --> 00:38:18,440
 kad spomenuo si muškarca na koljenima,

1212
00:38:18,440 --> 00:38:20,760
 obično kada vidimo neku sliku

1213
00:38:20,760 --> 00:38:22,120
 muškarca na koljenima

1214
00:38:22,120 --> 00:38:25,740
 i kada sami kleknemo,

1215
00:38:25,740 --> 00:38:27,820
 sad ovo iz perspektive muškarca,

1216
00:38:27,820 --> 00:38:30,460
 kada nas netko vidi da klećimo,

1217
00:38:30,460 --> 00:38:32,720
 obično je to,

1218
00:38:32,720 --> 00:38:34,460
 kada gledamo iz perspektive svijeta,

1219
00:38:34,460 --> 00:38:36,820
 kada vidiš muškarca na koljenima,

1220
00:38:36,820 --> 00:38:38,520
 to je onda muškarac,

1221
00:38:38,620 --> 00:38:40,040
 koji je bespomoćan,

1222
00:38:40,040 --> 00:38:42,560
 koji moli za milost,

1223
00:38:42,560 --> 00:38:45,320
 koji je poražen,

1224
00:38:45,320 --> 00:38:47,480
 koji je onako utučen,

1225
00:38:47,480 --> 00:38:52,120
 koji više nema ništa od sebe.

1226
00:38:55,120 --> 00:38:59,940
 a koja je razlika kada jedan katolički muškarac kleći ili plaće?

1227
00:39:00,660 --> 00:39:01,460
 ili jedno i drugo?

1228
00:39:01,460 --> 00:39:05,320
 da, moguće i u kombinaciji.

1229
00:39:05,940 --> 00:39:09,120
 pa, ogromna je razlika, ogromna je razlika.

1230
00:39:10,420 --> 00:39:13,300
 mislim to svaki muškarac mora odgovoriti za sebe,

1231
00:39:13,300 --> 00:39:14,680
 znači neki su emocionalni,

1232
00:39:14,680 --> 00:39:15,520
 neki manje,

1233
00:39:15,520 --> 00:39:18,220
 neki plaću ko kišna godina,

1234
00:39:18,220 --> 00:39:22,940
 neki su zatvoreni ko cisterna, bunar,

1235
00:39:22,940 --> 00:39:24,000
 što god hoćete,

1236
00:39:24,000 --> 00:39:26,060
 ali, eto,

1237
00:39:26,060 --> 00:39:27,540
 ja osobno, evo,

1238
00:39:27,540 --> 00:39:29,140
 znam se rasplakat,

1239
00:39:29,140 --> 00:39:30,680
 ako nešto bude dirljivo,

1240
00:39:30,680 --> 00:39:31,960
 emocionalno,

1241
00:39:31,960 --> 00:39:35,080
 znam i poteći suza isto kada molim,

1242
00:39:35,080 --> 00:39:36,260
 recimo kad molim krunicu,

1243
00:39:36,260 --> 00:39:37,400
 kad molim san,

1244
00:39:37,860 --> 00:39:43,320
 znači kada sam nekoj u četiri zida svoje kuće,

1245
00:39:43,320 --> 00:39:44,380
 znači kad me niko ne vidi,

1246
00:39:44,380 --> 00:39:45,860
 znači same,

1247
00:39:45,860 --> 00:39:47,240
 suze same počnu teći,

1248
00:39:47,240 --> 00:39:47,900
 ja ne znam zašto,

1249
00:39:47,900 --> 00:39:50,000
 ali jednostavno to bude tako,

1250
00:39:50,000 --> 00:39:51,020
 nemam pojma,

1251
00:39:51,020 --> 00:39:55,220
 ali nije sramota plakat,

1252
00:39:55,220 --> 00:39:56,760
 nije sramota za plakat,

1253
00:39:56,760 --> 00:39:58,600
 znači nije sramota pustiti suzu,

1254
00:39:58,600 --> 00:40:04,680
 tako da ne bi ja rekao da pravi muškarac ne plaće

1255
00:40:04,680 --> 00:40:06,540
 ili da nike ne bi trebalo plakat,

1256
00:40:06,540 --> 00:40:10,960
 nego jednostavno može oni za plakat,

1257
00:40:10,960 --> 00:40:12,800
 ali recimo za prave stvari,

1258
00:40:12,800 --> 00:40:14,860
 nekad o gadinamu gubi ili

1259
00:40:14,860 --> 00:40:20,580
 kad se zatvore birtije zbog korona,

1260
00:40:20,580 --> 00:40:23,780
 znači ako je neki pravi opravdan razlog,

1261
00:40:23,780 --> 00:40:25,220
 onda naravno, znači nema problema.

1262
00:40:25,220 --> 00:40:28,720
 Ono, rođenje djeteta čovje će...

1263
00:40:28,720 --> 00:40:29,180
 Plaći.

1264
00:40:29,180 --> 00:40:30,580
 Plaći, plaći.

1265
00:40:30,580 --> 00:40:30,860
 Udri.

1266
00:40:30,860 --> 00:40:36,260
 Znači, a klečanje?

1267
00:40:36,540 --> 00:40:40,340
 Pa da, da, zašto ne?

1268
00:40:40,340 --> 00:40:41,020
 Zašto ne?

1269
00:40:41,020 --> 00:40:44,460
 Mislim da je to jako dobar pokazati drugima.

1270
00:40:44,460 --> 00:40:49,160
 Recimo, evo sad baš lazi na pamet jedna priča,

1271
00:40:49,160 --> 00:40:50,960
 odnosno svećanstva Damira Stojića.

1272
00:40:50,960 --> 00:40:56,660
 Dakle, njemu je narasao taj žar da služi u crkvi,

1273
00:40:56,720 --> 00:41:01,140
 da postane svećenik i da uđe u dublju modu kada je vidio svog oca

1274
00:41:01,140 --> 00:41:05,760
 kako kleči, kada moli, kako kleči u crkvi.

1275
00:41:05,760 --> 00:41:10,980
 Tako da, to je nešto jako, jako poticajno.

1276
00:41:10,980 --> 00:41:15,160
 Izbilja pokazuje tu neku poniznost,

1277
